author: Huawei
description:
At #HUAWEICONNECT Europe 2025 in Madrid, experts, leaders, and partners explored how AI, 5G, and green technologies are accelerating Europe's digital and green transitions.

From new innovation milestones to SME-focused solutions and talent development, #Huawei reaffirmed its commitment to "in Europe, for Europe" as it works with partners to build an all-intelligent, greener future.

Watch now to catch the event highlights and learn more about the event at https://bit.ly/481umKF
title: HUAWEI CONNECT Europe 2025: Shaping a Greener, All Intelligent Europe

title: HUAWEI XMAGE Awards 2025 Ceremony & Annual Exhibition - Illuminating Paris

author: Huawei
description:
At the #Huawei Innovation & Intellectual Property Forum 2025, Etienne Sanz de Acedo, CEO of the International Trademark Association, highlighted Huawei's leadership in the global innovation ecosystem and how Huawei provides real value for consumers today.

The event brought together global experts to discuss how openness and strong IP protection drive long-term innovation and highlight progress across key technology domains. 

Read more about #IPR2025 at https://bit.ly/49UwQgk 

Watch the livestream replay at https://bit.ly/4i6xeu5 #IPMatters
title: Open Innovation: Huawei Innovation & Intellectual Property Forum 2025
